===Etymology===
The sound /ɛ/ followed by the sound of the letter, by analogy with other letter names, such as those of [[f]], [[l]], and [[m]]. <!-- ; its shape is derived from [[d]] with an added cross-stroke. [This is irrelevant to the etymology of the word]-->

